  "A 2D game engine needs to project a shadow. An object is at height h = 10 and a light source is at position (20, 30). If the ground is y = 0, at what x-coordinate does the shadow of the object at (5, 10) fall on the ground?": "",
  "x = 5 - (5-20) * (10/(30-10)) = 5 + 15*(10/20) = 12.5": "",
  "x = 20 - (20-5) * (30/(30-10)) = 20 - 22.5 = -2.5": "",
  "x = 5 - 15 * (10/30) = 0": "",
  "x = 15": "",
  "The light ray goes from (20, 30) through (5, 10). Parametrically: x = 20 + t(5-20) = 20-15t, y = 30 + t(10-30) = 30-20t. When y = 0: 30-20t = 0, t = 3/2. x = 20-15(3/2) = 20-22.5 = -2.5.": ""
